      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 3.",
      "rationale": "The validation activities replicate the ASTM F1717 test protocol that constitutes the intended use scenario for the computational model. The experimental constructs are production-representative and the loading conditions match the regulatory standard. Achieved level 3 reflects high fidelity correspondence between validation scenario and intended model application as described in the claim and requirement documentation."
